		"description": "<p>At 7th level, you gain one of the following features:</p><p><em><strong>Trained Eyes.&nbsp;</strong></em>You gain darkvision out to a range of 30 feet, or if you already have it, the range of your darkvision increases by 30 feet.</p><p>Additionally, you gain an expertise die to perceive, detect and locate traps.</p><p><em><strong>Trained Feet.</strong></em>&nbsp;Moving through nonmagical difficult terrain and magical difficult terrain that you have created costs you no extra movement.</p><p><em><strong>Trained Mind.&nbsp;</strong></em>You gain proficiency with your choice of either Arcana, Culture, History, or Religion. If you are already proficient in the chosen skill, you instead gain an expertise die.</p>",
